title: Colombia's TuHabi, latest property tech 'unicorn,' touts $200 mln funding - Reuters
content: Colombia's TuHabi, latest property tech 'unicorn,' touts $200 mln funding  Reuters
description: Colombia's TuHabi became the country's first property technology "unicorn," or company with a $1 billion valuation, after announcing a fresh $200 million funding round earlier this week.
